=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=charlemaine>Charlemaine</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(4/11/02 8:57:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1719.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two trolls need a hand in kunark.</span><hr size=1> I'd be weary about doing anything for eternal gartitude from trolls.... <br><br>&gt;raises an eye suspiciously&lt;<br><br>OOC: Just razzing you guys. I can't bind so I can't help you out, otherwise I would. But that spelling mistake was just too delicious to pass up. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usllackblader.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sllack Blader</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(4/12/02 8:03:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1719.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two trolls need a hand in kunark.</span><hr size=1> I reckon there is a soulbinder in Overthere. I may be wrong. Anyone know? <p><center><a href="http://www.kanebayle.com"><img src="http://www.kanebayle.com/love2.gif"></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uavalisschadenfreude.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Avalis Schadenfreude</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 93<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(4/12/02 8:28:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://