n><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(4/14/02 10:37:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1719.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two trolls need a hand in kunark.</span><hr size=1> If you ever get caught in a death loop, pull the plug, login another char (or call a friend to) and petition.<br><br>But knowing that kaesora's is bindable right outside - holy cow that would be a very desirable place to play in the high 20's to high 30's.<br><br>I have always enjoyed the look and feel of that dungeon. <p><center><a href="http://www.kanebayle.com"><img src="http://www.kanebayle.com/love2.gif"></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=1719.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=1719.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1719.topic&index=10><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.threadControl?topicID=1719.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1719.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1719.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" v